data.description: Beautiful country setting just across from the Lawrenceburg Golf and Country Club. This home is situated on over 2 acres of land bordering Crowson Creek which backs up to David Crockett State Park. Many updates including new paint in most rooms, new kitchen and updated bathrooms. 4 bedrooms (all with walk-in closets! One is currently used as an office and one as a sewing room), 2.5 baths, hardwood floors throughout, lots of closet space, large bedrooms, full basement with outside access and perfect for a workshop. Sit on your screened in porch and see plenty of wildlife while listening to the soothing sounds of the creek below. Very secluded yet close to town and Hwy 64 bypass.
